  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the efficacy and safety of reserpine for the treatment
      of cocaine dependence.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To assess the efficacy and safety of reserpine in reducing cocaine use in subjects with
      cocaine dependence. This is a double-blind, placebo-controlled, parallel-group design with a
      2 week baseline period.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
